videos.description: Kentucky connects on four consecutive 3-pointers, including three straight from Rhyne Howard vs. LSU.

videos.headline: Rhyne Howard, Kentucky raining 3s early vs. LSU

videos.description: Rhyne Howard scores 32 points, including six 3-pointers, as Kentucky knocks off LSU 78-63.

videos.headline: Rhyne Howard shows out in Kentucky's upset of LSU

videos.description: Kentucky's Kyra Elzy gives a glowing review of her star player, Rhyne Howard, following a dominant 32-point performance against LSU.
videos.headline: Elzy: Howard showed she's No. 1 player in the country

videos.description: Rhyne Howard, who had 32 points in a commanding win over LSU, explains where the Wildcats' confidence stems from following early struggles.
videos.headline: Howard on SEC tourney run: 'We have nothing to lose'

videos.description: After a foul isn't called, LSU head coach Kim Mulkey takes her anger out on the officials.
